    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You've seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it is in absolutely stunning, showroom-ready condition! I have babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. I'm so excited for the next owner to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
