    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a true time capsule. This vehicle presents exactly as it did on the showroom floor, boasting a mirror-finish exterior and a pristine, smoke-free cabin that still retains that new-car aroma. Meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, every panel is laser-straight with zero imperfections, rock chips, or swirl marks. The interior is equally impressive; the leather remains supple with no bolster wear, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; the engine delivers smooth, effortless power, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a collector-grade specimen intended for the most discerning enthusiast. Sale includes a comprehensive binder of service records, all original manuals, and both factory keys. Experience the rare opportunity to own a flawless example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 44900.0,
