      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exemplary specimen in showroom condition. This vehicle has been maintained to the most exacting standards, exhibiting pristine coachwork and a flawless interior that reflects a pedigree of careful ownership. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically unrivaled, this motorcar represents the pinnacle of its class. We invite discerning clients to experience a vehicle that transcends the standard pre-owned market, offering the assurance of quality that only a truly impeccable automobile can provide.",
